---
applyTo: "**/*.py"
---

When editing Python in this repository:

- Preserve the repository's existing module layout and naming patterns.
- Add type hints to new or changed public APIs.
- Prefer standard-library helpers before introducing a new dependency.
- Avoid import-time side effects unless the surrounding code already relies on them.
- Keep parsing, I/O, and business logic separated when it improves clarity.
- Update nearby tests when behavior changes.
